DocHive
=======

More documentatin will be coming soon. 

DocHive has 2 prerequisites, ImageMagick and Tesseract.

Compile Instructions
--------------------

### Windows

Install both prerequisites, for command line use, and update

(1) bin\convert.bat
(2) bin\tesseract.bat

with a path like 

"%PROGRAMFILES%\ImageMagick-6.7.8-Q16\Convert" 
or
"%PROGRAMFILES%\Tesseract-OCR\tesseract"

Compile the java program by executing compile.bat

Run a test with runtest.bat

### Linux

Install both prerequisites

Compile the java program by executing compile.sh

Run a test with runtest.sh

